name: Patetfiske
description:
Patetfiske is a very simple and relaxing fishing game. The game is completely played with the mouse and can be played by anyone.

FEATURES:

  • 32 unique sea creatures to collect
  • Almost 19 seconds of music
  • Day/night cycle
  • Saving and loading
  • Window size customization
  • Funny birds to click
  • Realistic sounds
